<DealerHubLayout title="New Designer Onboarding | Pinnacle Sales" activeSection="Designer Onboarding">

<h1>New Designer Onboarding</h1>
<p class="page-subtitle">Your training roadmap from product orientation to placing your first orders with confidence.</p>

<h2>Step 1 — Onboarding Training Session 1 (In-Person)</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="do-1">✓</span><div><strong>Product & sales orientation (~90 min)</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Your territory manager will schedule an in-person session at your showroom. Covers cabinet construction and SKUs, finish overview, quoting tips, and competitive positioning. Target: within 10 days of receiving your samples.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Step 2 — Onboarding Training Session 2 (Live 2020 Webinar)</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="do-2">✓</span><div><strong>Hands-on 2020 Design catalog walkthrough (~90 min)</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Live webinar covering WW Wood 2020 Design catalogs: catalog setup, spec rules, pricing, and order-form export. Our Dealer Success & 2020 Specialist will reach out to schedule. Target: 1 week after your in-person session.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Step 3 — Placing Your First Orders</h2>
<ul class="checklist">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="do-3">✓</span><div><strong>Submit your first order for review</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Your first 3-4 projects require a pre-order review before being sent to the factory. Email your order to our Dealer Success Specialist for review — expect a 48-hour turnaround. After your first few projects, you're cleared to order independently with <a href="/dealer-hub/submit">design reviews</a> available as needed.</span></div></li>
</ul>

